Package org.youscope.clientinterfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClientAddonProvider
    Provider with which YouScop client addons can be constructed.
    YouScopeClient
    Interface through which an addon can access the client.
    YouScopeFrame
    Generalized interface for frames.
    YouScopeFrameListener  
    YouScopeProperties
    Interface through which an addon can save properties as well as access the properties of the YouScope client.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FramePositionStorageType
    Enum defining how frame positions should be stored.
    StandardProperty
    Standard (default) properties of YouScope.
